{"tid":373801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台會在明日日間考慮發出一號戒備信號","createTime":"2017-08-25T09:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T15:33:58.000Z","uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c77329050d61b428250cfa3c9016c021d0c6bb1","tid":373801,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"預料熱帶風暴帕卡會橫過呂宋，於明日（星期六）進入南海，天文台會在明日日間考慮發出一號戒備信號。<br />\n<br />\n受到呂宋的地形影響，帕卡在橫過呂宋後的路徑和強度變化仍有變數。帕卡會採取偏西北方向移向廣東西部，但相比天鴿可能會離香港較遠。本港風力在星期日會增強，並間中有狂風大驟雨。<br />\n<br />\n市民應做好防風措施，並清理水渠以防水浸。與天鴿相關的清理工作亦應盡快完成。<br />\n<br />\n2017年08月25日17時30分更新"},{"pid":"0e02df90fed650c49d0e45b736a9f0e8eb51e8f6","tid":373801,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:40:12.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa76e9da05d400ff881e526974b88a469e371b0","tid":373801,"uid":110969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清你坐完時光機？"},{"pid":"0262c3f3db105af0d1ec15ee9376a2c28caf20ab","tid":373801,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T23:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清你坐完時光機？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44229609d0fad551da7c3729ed29cd8907505b8b","tid":373801,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7285ba2ba9814f63872934f936a75b93c520a15","tid":373801,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d137a1a2a46310379c18819c613696450d8042f"